import * as React from 'react';
import TextField from '@mui/material/TextField';
import Autocomplete from '@mui/material/Autocomplete';
import { Box } from '@mui/material';

export default function FreeSolo() {

    const exercises = [
        { title: 'Dumbell Press' },
        { title: 'Inclined Dumbell Press' },
        { title: 'Declined Dumbell Press' },
        { title: 'Bench Press' },
        { title: 'Inclined Bench Press' },
        { title: 'Declined Bench press' },
        { title: 'Dumbell flies' },
        { title: 'Inclined Dumbell Flies' },
        { title: 'Declined Dumbell Flies' },
        { title: 'Cable flies' },
        { title: 'Dumbell Military Press' },
        { title: 'Barbell Military Press' },
        { title: 'Dumbell front rise' },
        { title: 'Lateral Flies' },
        { title: 'Rope Triceps Pushdown' },
        { title: 'Barbell Triceps Pushdown' },
        { title: 'Cable Overhead Triceps Extensions' },
        { title: 'Overhead Triceps Extensions' },
        { title: 'Triceps Kickbacks' },
        { title: 'Dips' },
        { title: 'Skullcrushers' },
        { title: 'Dumbell Posterior Fly ' },
        { title: 'Cable row' },
        { title: 'Machine Row' },
        { title: 'Incline Machine Row' },
        { title: 'Dumbell Row' },
        { title: 'Inclined Dumbell Row' },
        { title: 'Barbell Row' },
        { title: 'Lat Pulldown' },
        { title: 'Pull Ups' },
        { title: 'Dumbell Bicep Curl' },
        { title: 'Barbell Bicep Curl' },
        { title: 'W Dumbell Bicep Curl' },
        { title: 'W Barbell Bicep Curl' },
        { title: 'Machine Row' },

      ];

  return (
    <Box sx={{ width: '70%'}}>
      <Autocomplete
        freeSolo
        id="free-solo-2-demo"
        disableClearable
        options={exercises.map((option) => option.title)}
        renderInput={(params) => (
          <TextField
            {...params}
            label="Search Exercises"
            InputProps={{
              ...params.InputProps,
              type: 'search',
            }}
          />
        )}
      />
      </Box>
  );
}
